{"tid":1635062,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[核爆級］教育局要點人頭 點解無人理！？","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:04:24.000Z","uid":178471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad5a83d0dfebde064c7195a93b5e49834fd8487","tid":1635062,"uid":178471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"你班柒頭 仲9下9下<br />\n教育局話要交人數<br />\n有幾多學生戴口罩番學<br />\n話唔會留個人資料你地就唔撚驚！？<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦點咩撚野人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個政府講幾句解釋你就信<br />\n就唔撚理下化？<br />\n佢地做咩都係有陰謀有策略<br />\n<br />\n由一開始政府Popo都將矛頭指向示威者<br />\n大部分都係學生 <br />\n<br />\n係「學生」啊！懵丙<br />\n教育局已經唔係教育為重 <br />\n係政府既耳目<br />\n係監控為實 <br />\n<br />\n佢依家就係想統計下<br />\n邊區邊間學校所謂「極端暴力分子」<br />\n再逐一擊破 同 去查你地啊！<br />\n懵丙！！<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講我病唔得啊！<br />\n政府已經將口罩同反政府劃上等號！！<br />\n<br />\n統計完可以做咩？<br />\n咪派多D Popo 看守你地<br />\n來緊既抗爭未開波 可能就被禁熄<br />\nBig brother is watching u<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地進化時<br />\n政府都會進化<br />\n任何正面文章 同我全部反面讀<br />\n「唔好信啊！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學生要自保<br />\n學生一係一齊全部戴<br />\n一係全部都唔戴<br />\n麻煩學生們自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比佢地得到任何有意思既統計數字！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時就麻撚煩<br />\n<br />\n到時周圍都係Popo 陪你番放工<br />\n真係安全到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e547a8cb1bae504e00af91488216209b54505b9e","tid":1635062,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>極度譴責政府主動將政治帶入校園</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0a2915a2760a610936abf10c10e52c6b29960731","tid":1635062,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:44:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">學生無罪</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"81ebc44eb3a86ff485caaeb53b367be3cb8e6ebd","tid":1635062,"uid":167825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"399578d4b33b75fbb9cc73b9de7f98c46391ccee","tid":1635062,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a937ef94de8f5ebc29ee783b0180d739f48a5203","tid":1635062,"uid":303508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"461aa18aef0739e988704b7af26c2d11ae3aa4e6","tid":1635062,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:02:23.000Z","msg":"個個都戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2abd082da35aa0335cb69b8f6fa9b7d6b959dfd","tid":1635062,"uid":323797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"新口號：和勇相連 永不割蓆！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634504\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634504</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打幫幫手討論下要唔要新口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7iSSOZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7iSSOZK.jpg&h=4440f0bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b5e340457cb314221f0c538804ede0994d0eb01","tid":1635062,"uid":328405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5131249f872989a29a1f0ea837692ddc6db117e","tid":1635062,"uid":263434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"齊齊自修IAL 棄 DSE <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075cc8a33bedcbf41195e9f702674a00abcee25a","tid":1635062,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"有冇人諗過為何教育局可以干涉學校?<br />\n<br />\n因為教育局合併左教育署，而教育署係有權管理公立學校<br />\n<br />\n教育作為專業，唔應該比政治任命官員控制<br />\n<br />\n建議參考醫管局，成立公校管理局，由管理局監督各公立學校自行管理校務"}]}